data.description: WELCOME HOME to this beautiful low maintenance exterior ranch home in Sunshine Acres. Offering 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths on a landscaped corner lot. Kitchen remodeled several years ago, enlarged the area to now include a walk-in pantry and eat-in area. Granite countertop island, kitchen cabinets and flooring replaced. kitchen refrigerator, range, dishwasher and wine cooler all remain with the home. Primary bedroom with remodeled bathroom. Full finished basement with plenty of room to entertain guests or watch your favorite movies or sports. Plenty of storage space too! Half bathroom for convenience too. Fully-fenced back yard, attached 2 car garage with keypad and 2 remotes AND a carport too. ADT alarm system in place the buyer can transfer service into their name. Sold as-is.
